{"id": 484, "title": "Ticket #484: Memory size incorrect for libvirt-based VMs", "description": "<blockquote>\nCondor stores the memory for a VM in the job ad in megabytes, but the libvirt VM configuration file expects the memory in kilobytes. The VM GAHP isn't converting the job ad value as it should. Matt fixed this in 7.3, but the problem has now been noticed in 7.2.</blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n</blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "", "attachments": "<html><head></head><body></body></html>", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2009-May-14 14:58</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/34dac17213b7fa5b3bd68cc606f4a10fbf9d08c7\">[24786]</a></span>: Document Xen memory size bug fix (gittrac <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=484\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('484'); return false;\" title=\"Memory size incorrect for libvirt-based VMs\">#484</a></span>)  (By Jaime Frey )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2009-May-14 14:46</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/b8d80f1f175fe159ca31709f5718585a3fb1aa32\">[14689]</a></span>: Fix memory size for xen VMs libvirt expects the VM's memory in kilobytes. The job ad stores the memory in megabytes. The VM GAHP needs to convert when writing the configuration file for libvirt. gittrac <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=484\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('484'); return false;\" title=\"Memory size incorrect for libvirt-based VMs\">#484</a></span>  (By Jaime Frey )</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>", "type": "defect", "last_change": "2010-Jan-31 08:36", "status": "resolved", "created": "2009-May-14 14:45", "fixed_version": "2009-May-14 14:45", "broken_version": "v070200", "priority": "2", "subsystem": "VM", "assigned_to": "jfrey", "derived_from": "", "creator": "jfrey", "rust": "a19280", "customer_group": "other", "visibility": "public", "notify": "", "due_date": ""}